        }
      ],
      "message": "psbt: preserve proprietary fields when combining PSBTs\n\nCombinePSBTs currently preserves unknown records but drops proprietary records at the global, input, and output levels because the Merge() paths never union m_proprietary.\n\nPreserve proprietary records in PartiallySignedTransaction::Merge(), PSBTInput::Merge(), and PSBTOutput::Merge() so combine/merge keeps all PSBT key-value data.",
      "committer": {
        "name": "w0xlt",
        "email": "94266259+w0xlt@users.noreply.github.com",
        "date": "2026-03-24T22:48:32Z"
